      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "9394f38dfa784a07",
      "text": "Largely because others have convinced me that virtually nothing has yet been written about applying concepts from ethology to the management of organizations. That is strange to say the least. You will have to decide for yourself whether I should have prevented the publication of this book."
